bit has a lot of meanings to geeks, so what.

bit means for average people:
- something very small, that 100 satoshi is. 
- part of the name Bitcoin
- easy to get conversion 1 coin = 1 million bits = 1 Bitcoin

Regards,

Tamas Blummer
